Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.20,0:01:47.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍哥哥 快點快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.27,0:01:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.14,0:01:50.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用這麼急
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.14,0:01:51.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大蛇!湯圓！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.74,0:01:55.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位都同時說出口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.81,0:01:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.58,0:02:00.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是人山人海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.45,0:02:01.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是那當然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.39,0:02:04.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,墨田川界邊\N現在是最有名的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.19,0:02:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們兩個人怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.22,0:02:09.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.79,0:02:14.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好啊 我們進去看看！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.06,0:02:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這一定是騙小孩的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.43,0:02:17.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不是小孩子嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.64,0:02:18.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.40,0:02:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,進去吧 進去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.01,0:02:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,羽毛在動…有雷獸呢.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.85,0:02:29.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.81,0:02:32.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是長脖子的妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.72,0:02:38.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,…狐貍女人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.29,0:02:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,…狐貍男人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.83,0:02:43.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妖怪 妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.16,0:02:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像很快樂的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.03,0:02:47.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想是很害怕吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.10,0:02:48.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恩 果然是這樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.97,0:02:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這樣的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.77,0:02:55.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這邊山豬的羽毛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.81,0:02:58.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是和線綁起來用拉的而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.18,0:03:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是騙小孩子的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.24,0:03:02.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.48,0:03:05.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對阿薰她們好像剛剛好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.78,0:03:07.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.95,0:03:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妖怪..怎麼了….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.55,0:03:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好可憐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.42,0:03:13.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是因為你！嚇弱女子所以.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.52,0:03:15.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不做了..這種生意.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.00,0:03:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第十七話\N飛向夢想 炮美女瑪利的冒險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.27,0:03:28.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇 這是什麼呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.31,0:03:29.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人好多喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.71,0:03:30.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們去看一看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.87,0:03:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也許有值得看的價值
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.94,0:03:35.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是惠比須炮術團…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.55,0:04:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡 今天又有烏鴉在叫了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.56,0:04:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對面那間小屋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.46,0:04:24.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開始後每天就這樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.66,0:04:27.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡！那個炮彈小姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.23,0:04:29.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把我們的客人都拉到那裏去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.40,0:04:32.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家好！今天非常歡迎各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.60,0:04:34.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到我的惠比須炮術團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.64,0:04:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是非常的謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.84,0:04:38.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼在場的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.34,0:04:41.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請看讓各位久等的人間炮彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.31,0:04:44.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這小姑娘瑪利\N作為飛彈射向那目標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.95,0:04:46.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請鼓掌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.69,0:04:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.29,0:04:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟禰彥一樣年紀的小姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.73,0:04:57.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.04,0:05:10.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒關係嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.47,0:05:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火藥的調合是關鍵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.04,0:05:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太強的話很危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.75,0:05:16.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太弱也不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.98,0:05:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼開始吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.92,0:05:22.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一二三
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.20,0:05:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好厲害 好厲害\N明治炮彈姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.81,0:05:43.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,親子不配合的很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.71,0:05:45.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就沒辦法進行得順利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.64,0:05:47.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.14,0:05:48.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.58,0:05:50.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飛了飛了…..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.55,0:05:56.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓開讓開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.32,0:05:58.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回去！給我回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.96,0:06:00.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.66,0:06:03.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心 為什麼阻止他呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.76,0:06:06.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們先看一下情形吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.43,0:06:09.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,墨田先生你要做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.90,0:06:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我非常關心你們的生意 做得好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.40,0:06:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你雖然已經獨立了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.77,0:06:18.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,畢竟以前 曾經在我們的小屋待過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.98,0:06:21.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這件事不需要你的關心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.01,0:06:23.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我應該已經交出證明文件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.98,0:06:25.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,取得獨立了才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.38,0:06:28.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對 所以忘了就很傷腦筋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.35,0:06:31.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在獨立之前曾向我借過錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.32,0:06:33.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有一些沒有還
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.66,0:06:35.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,錢的話我會還給你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.13,0:06:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天半額 剩下的明天還！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.69,0:06:39.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎是嗎 這樣就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.66,0:06:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,約定的日期到明天的晚上為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.13,0:06:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你應該明白的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.84,0:06:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不還的話就不要有異意\N回到我的小屋去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.04,0:06:51.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回去吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.01,0:06:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.85,0:06:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.82,0:07:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼今天我等你來還錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.62,0:07:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.32,0:07:05.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,煙蒂的火不好好處理不行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.32,0:07:07.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是 對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.12,0:07:09.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不小心不行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.13,0:07:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼傢伙呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.76,0:07:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥現在開始去把他打倒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.90,0:07:17.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快去吧 禰彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.34,0:07:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不在了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.17,0:07:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.17,0:07:22.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼時候跑去的….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.91,0:07:26.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我 我是明神禰彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.91,0:07:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,女孩子還敢從大炮飛出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.85,0:07:30.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的很勇敢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.55,0:07:32.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我非常的感動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.38,0:07:33.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是瑪利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.82,0:07:37.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你幫我 小禰彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.52,0:07:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要加上「小」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.73,0:07:49.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你喜歡上那個人了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.93,0:07:51.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才不是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.67,0:07:53.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是覺得那個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.57,0:07:55.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用再打馬虎眼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.87,0:07:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不是喜歡紅屋的小燕嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.87,0:08:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還真容易喜歡人家呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.41,0:08:02.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要去哪裏呢 禰彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.85,0:08:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,散步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.91,0:08:08.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了 讓夜風吹一吹\N頭腦也許會冷靜一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.09,0:08:13.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是 散步真是差勁的藉口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.22,0:08:17.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他非常在意那孩子的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.19,0:08:20.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是禰彥的男子漢氣概
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.94,0:08:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小心一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.91,0:08:32.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 等一下 那個錢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.64,0:08:35.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.09,0:08:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.26,0:08:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.96,0:08:50.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.93,0:08:53.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們對爸爸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.30,0:08:55.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那又怎樣呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.63,0:08:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有誰…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.67,0:09:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放開我爸爸.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.71,0:09:08.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正明天也不能表演了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.88,0:09:11.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有回到墨田屋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.52,0:09:13.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放開那隻手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.15,0:09:15.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 小禰彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.69,0:09:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要加「小」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.66,0:09:22.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這傢伙！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.83,0:09:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是神谷活心流的第一位徒弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.36,0:09:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明神禰彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.46,0:09:28.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.17,0:09:36.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.57,0:09:39.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你給我記住！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.28,0:09:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.44,0:09:41.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.95,0:09:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我爸爸被壓在下面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.31,0:09:45.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.72,0:09:52.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,短時間內不能動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.99,0:09:56.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是大夫 我不去把錢拿回來不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.59,0:09:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有用的 爸爸！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.93,0:10:00.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,墨田屋一定會佯裝不知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.10,0:10:02.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我等一下會去報警的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.87,0:10:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸慢慢的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.23,0:10:06.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行 沒那個錢不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.80,0:10:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使是逞強 明天不表演 錢就
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.77,0:10:11.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是 是啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.14,0:10:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那樣也算是還了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.84,0:10:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把木材弄倒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.11,0:10:15.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也是那些傢伙幹的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.71,0:10:18.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有任何證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.15,0:10:19.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他一定會說是事故的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.95,0:10:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,墨田屋就是這種傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.15,0:10:25.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我跟我爸爸\N就是因為墨田屋做壞事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.89,0:10:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以才獨立的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.39,0:10:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.46,0:10:30.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙會這麼蠻橫無理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.13,0:10:32.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那…那麼表演呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.83,0:10:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是說不能動嗎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.80,0:10:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸 我明天一個人做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.17,0:10:39.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,告訴我火藥的調合方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.34,0:10:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,外行人是沒辦法辦到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.14,0:10:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒關係的 我做得來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.04,0:10:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太危險了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.34,0:10:46.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火藥的調合一有差錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.21,0:10:48.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,腳也許會被炸到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.55,0:10:49.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.08,0:10:53.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不想讓你遇到這種危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.15,0:10:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也幫忙 所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.39,0:10:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.25,0:10:59.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要回到墨田屋就解決了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.76,0:11:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火藥的調合\N是不是藥量不一樣呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.83,0:11:05.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果告訴我的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.53,0:11:07.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也許我做得到吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.34,0:11:19.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有血的味道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.84,0:11:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你很喜歡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.44,0:11:23.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比蘋果的臭味還
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.91,0:11:27.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊..特別是被自己殺死的人的血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.62,0:11:28.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.62,0:11:30.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你覺得怎樣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.12,0:11:33.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我嗎..對血沒有什麼興趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.32,0:11:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.49,0:11:36.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對於你的細小的脖子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.29,0:11:39.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很想這樣的擰看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.26,0:11:41.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.23,0:11:44.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你成為我的靶的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.63,0:11:46.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的 一個客人也沒有！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.50,0:11:48.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且今天期限也到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.24,0:11:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,次郎那傢伙是沒辦法表演了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.34,0:11:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那這樣的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.44,0:11:57.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他一定會哭著來說\N請原諒我 墨田屋先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.28,0:12:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都是我的錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.05,0:12:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.32,0:12:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是不能安心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.15,0:12:04.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是只有她女兒一個人的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.42,0:12:06.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是沒辦法擊大炮的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.12,0:12:07.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是個不甘示弱的孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.52,0:12:08.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一個人也會做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.83,0:12:10.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了安心起見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.96,0:12:11.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是 是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.90,0:12:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種困惑的事就交給我們吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.67,0:12:17.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果交給你們這些人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.17,0:12:20.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼最重要的炮彈姑娘\N就不能使用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.47,0:12:26.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歡迎光臨 歡迎光臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.41,0:12:28.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那邊也有！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.48,0:12:30.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這邊也有！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.41,0:12:31.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是只有讓你看東西而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.58,0:12:33.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可愛的少女轟隆一聲！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.42,0:12:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從大炮飛出去 人間炮彈！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.92,0:12:39.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然 可是到此為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.59,0:12:43.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.43,0:12:44.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們來看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.56,0:12:46.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定會讓它成功的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.46,0:12:48.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼…在哪裏呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.47,0:12:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.30,0:12:50.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你來做什麼呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.03,0:12:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那還用說嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.04,0:12:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然是來看炮彈姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.41,0:12:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也許不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.64,0:13:00.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是看小瑪利嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.28,0:13:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是一樣的嗎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.61,0:13:04.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,結果你是來嘲笑我的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.21,0:13:06.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看起來像那種男人嗎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.42,0:13:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.19,0:13:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.92,0:13:11.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不得了了 禰彥！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.39,0:13:12.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了 瑪利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.66,0:13:13.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.76,0:13:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火藥沒有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.36,0:13:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道被誰偷走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.96,0:13:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.56,0:13:18.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼辦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.66,0:13:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說怎麼辦\N客人都已經來很多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.17,0:13:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,煙火屋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.77,0:13:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這界川裏有很多的煙火屋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.77,0:13:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,東邊向西走就能買到火藥了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.11,0:13:31.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.78,0:13:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.08,0:13:37.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有禰彥 不知道是哪種火藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.98,0:13:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來得及嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.22,0:13:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遲了的話\N就會引起客人的騷動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.82,0:13:45.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到那時候 只有由我們來表演了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.62,0:13:47.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不做不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.22,0:13:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會不好意思的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.86,0:13:51.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼我要…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.10,0:13:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點開始！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.43,0:13:59.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們已經付錢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.74,0:14:02.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓各位久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.11,0:14:04.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有點不自然.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.51,0:14:06.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不做不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.28,0:14:08.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天真的非常感謝各位光臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.91,0:14:11.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惠比須炮術團！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.51,0:14:14.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼在人間炮彈開始之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.48,0:14:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天有特別的表演要給各位看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.55,0:14:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒問題吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.16,0:14:20.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒問題的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.19,0:14:21.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有劍哥哥在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.26,0:14:23.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是 是啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.66,0:14:26.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,首先
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.50,0:14:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由緋村染之助跟相藥染太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.43,0:14:30.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來表演走大球雨傘轉小球表演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.73,0:14:32.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼 請吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.47,0:14:35.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的要做嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.34,0:14:37.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要做了就會成功呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.67,0:14:38.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.18,0:14:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像在坐船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.91,0:14:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.82,0:14:50.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心哥哥 加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.45,0:14:52.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加油 劍哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.39,0:14:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之 快 快點！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.82,0:14:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要去了 劍心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.59,0:14:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.50,0:15:08.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.21,0:15:10.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了 劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.81,0:15:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接受了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.94,0:15:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小生是染之助…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.25,0:15:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了染之助！再來…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.68,0:15:20.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好帥喔 染之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.92,0:15:23.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.49,0:15:25.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不快點不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.83,0:15:36.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瑪利….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.04,0:15:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小薰小姐 靶準備好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.04,0:15:44.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.61,0:15:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.94,0:15:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這麼說 我也不知道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.58,0:15:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是小薰小姐的指示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.25,0:15:50.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果中了怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.91,0:15:52.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以才要左之來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.52,0:15:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,混帳東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.62,0:15:57.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小姐 有自信嗎？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.42,0:16:00.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.39,0:16:04.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要逃走 劍心！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.87,0:16:12.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左…左之 有血…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.87,0:16:15.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心給我捉起來！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.31,0:16:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.94,0:16:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.64,0:16:18.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.58,0:16:19.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.81,0:16:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能等嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.84,0:16:21.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.68,0:16:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一下就好了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.75,0:16:23.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.75,0:16:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人間炮彈還沒有嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.38,0:16:28.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊 對啊 快點開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.72,0:16:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥 快點….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.89,0:16:33.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓開 讓開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.63,0:16:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.99,0:16:41.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走路不看前面是很危險的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.50,0:16:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你..你.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.43,0:16:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把那個袋子交給我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.00,0:16:47.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又是你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.40,0:16:50.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在胡言亂語扯些什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.74,0:16:54.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧 禰彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.15,0:16:56.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快追
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.88,0:16:58.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要把火藥交給他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.41,0:17:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喝…酒…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.58,0:17:04.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喝的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.75,0:17:10.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就像是火一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.16,0:17:12.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.20,0:17:19.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要唱了不要唱了 那麼奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.70,0:17:21.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人間飛彈到底怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.47,0:17:23.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不表演的話就退錢來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.21,0:17:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到此為止吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.58,0:17:29.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.45,0:17:31.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,黑田節的話我最有興趣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.55,0:17:32.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.92,0:17:34.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.92,0:17:36.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些傢伙…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.05,0:17:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.29,0:17:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.32,0:17:39.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,交給我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.92,0:17:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,變得有趣起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.16,0:17:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果給我乖乖的\N回到墨田屋就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.23,0:17:50.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼逞強的話\N我就讓你不能再表演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.37,0:17:53.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,違背墨田屋總兵衛的話\N會有什麼後果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.44,0:17:55.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我來告訴你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.54,0:18:03.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無聊的舉動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.95,0:18:04.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.72,0:18:08.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,交給我吧 左之！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.89,0:18:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼 喂喂！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.55,0:18:12.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經好久沒有殺人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.52,0:18:14.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我來把他們刺成串吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.19,0:18:16.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我來讓你們都骨折吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.66,0:18:20.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們的技術是為了與人爭嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.76,0:18:23.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要太小看他們三個比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.80,0:18:27.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,之前在墨田川 浮上士族的屍體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.30,0:18:28.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做這件事的是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.37,0:18:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.01,0:18:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這麼一回事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.98,0:18:33.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.21,0:18:35.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正只是給別人看而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.51,0:18:37.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用這個吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.01,0:18:38.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.02,0:18:40.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓各位久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.15,0:18:42.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在由緋村染之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.49,0:18:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為您表演飛天御劍流的奧秘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.22,0:18:51.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓你們看飛天御劍流傘的舞蹈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.46,0:18:52.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.83,0:18:54.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有這個嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.20,0:18:58.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飛天御劍流傘回轉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.50,0:19:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.91,0:19:04.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飛天御劍流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.21,0:19:05.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飛球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.44,0:19:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太棒了太棒了染之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.62,0:19:22.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 大炮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.66,0:19:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼嘛 猛豬突擊啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.56,0:19:27.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是野豬吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.93,0:19:29.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,混帳東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.70,0:19:32.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飛天御劍流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.97,0:19:34.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,閃避野豬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.80,0:19:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之 捉起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.84,0:19:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.64,0:19:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥 繩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.84,0:19:40.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.84,0:19:42.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,終於輪到我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.65,0:19:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不拔刀嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.65,0:19:46.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有傘就夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.32,0:19:47.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那種事可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.42,0:19:48.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點收拾他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.79,0:19:50.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點放馬過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.02,0:19:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.66,0:19:56.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.96,0:19:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飛天御劍流 落傘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.40,0:20:06.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這不是人類的技術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.57,0:20:09.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.38,0:20:17.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,星星 一閃一閃亮晶晶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.55,0:20:20.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逃走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.02,0:20:23.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會讓你逃走的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.89,0:20:25.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.86,0:20:26.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.10,0:20:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.93,0:20:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了 炮彈姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.84,0:20:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,染太郎也很有力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.14,0:20:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,染之助也很可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.58,0:20:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真嚇人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.48,0:20:50.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.85,0:20:52.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我受歡迎了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.68,0:20:55.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的 好嚇人喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.35,0:21:00.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,墨田屋總兵衛 你作這種壞事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.16,0:21:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人自首了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.42,0:21:02.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老老實實的招來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.83,0:21:09.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這件事算告一段落了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.53,0:21:14.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,客人都很喜歡\N以後要不要一起來表演呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.07,0:21:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.94,0:21:17.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正劍心跟左之助也很閒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.17,0:21:19.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我對小沙包也很拿手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.11,0:21:21.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.04,0:21:23.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們二人不要逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.51,0:21:26.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之 你留下來吧
