Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.95,0:21:28.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你留下來不是很好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.55,0:21:29.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就有一點…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.95,0:21:31.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋…

